Name: write in forum

description: the user can write into a certian forum

players: user, admin, DB

preconditions: logged in, forum you want to write into exist

Basic flow:
	1) Click on menu
	2) Menu pops up
	3) Click on forums
	4) Forum page shows up
  5) Choose a certain forum
  6) Forum shows up
  7) Write a message in text box
  8) Click post

alternate flow:-------------

exception flow: if the user click post without writing anything, the app will mark the missing information in red and require the user to complete it



post conditions:a new message was written in the forum
